data.description: Welcome to 74 Jackson Rd. in Lake City, AR! This charming and beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled on a spacious 0.51-acre lot. Step inside to discover a lovely kitchen, adored by the owners, boasting beautiful cabinets and stainless steel appliances, complete with a full pantry. The master suite is a true gem, showcasing stunning ceilings, a delightful bathroom, and a spacious walk-in closet. Outside, you'll find a wonderful wooden privacy fence, an attached two-car garage, and even a storm shelter for added peace of mind. The beautifully landscaped yard is the perfect finishing touch. Don't miss out on this must-see property!
